CORRUPTION; JAPAN -- CULTURE; BRIBERY; JAPAN -- TAXES; TAX EVASION; GIFTS; 
SECURITIES FRAUD; INSIDER INFORMATION; JAPAN -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
TAKESHITA, NOBORU 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
